5. PLUGINS (Workers uses the tool to run the code)

<maven-surefire-plugin>

Dependency = software/tools
Plugin = worker doing action


To run TestNg Execution
To generate reports
To run parallel executing 

-------------------------------------------------------

6. MAVEN BUILD LIFECYCLE

mvn clean   delete old files
mvn compile   compile java code
mvn test   executes TestNG tests & Generate the reports 

------------------------------------------------------


mvn clean test

1. Clean old target files
2. Validate project
3. Download missing dependencies
4. Compile source code
5. Compile test code
6. Execute TestNG/JUnit tests
7. Generate reports/results


pom.xml is the central configuration file in Maven which manages project metadata, dependencies, plugins, compiler settings and build lifecycle execution for the automation framework.